*simutrans-0.82.15.7 (12 Jan 2004)

  12 Jan 2004; Michael Sterrett <mr_bones_@gentoo.org>
  simutrans-0.82.15.7.ebuild:
  version bump (bug 38022)

  26 Nov 2003; Michael Sterrett <mr_bones_@gentoo.org>
  simutrans-0.82.10.ebuild:
  fix save directory permissions so saving games is allowed (bug 33573)
  more error checking/messages
  use sed-4

  18 Sep 2003; Michael Sterrett <msterret@gentoo.org> simutrans-0.81.0.ebuild,
  simutrans-0.82.10.ebuild, simutrans-0.82.3.ebuild, simutrans-0.82.5.ebuild:
  Mark simutrans-0.82.10 stable and clean out the old versions. All of these
  are, according to the author, "beta versions", but "quite playable".

